  <p>
    <ol label="1">
      <li>
        <p>You can copy the URL of almost any image in a browser by right clicking on the image and choosing <q>copy image URL</q>  or something similar.  Write an html page in the activecode window for this exercise that includes a header element giving a title to some image you find,  Then include the image in the page, sized appropriately,  and a paragraph that describes the image.</p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </p>
