  <p>
    <ol label="1">
      <li>
        <p>Make a table that looks like this:</p>
      </li>
    </ol>
  </p>
  <blockquote>
    <image source="challengetable.png" width="50%"/>
    <p>Hint, this is going to require both rowspan and columnspan.  Also, Do not try to do this all at once.  Start with the header, then move on to the rest of the table, working in small parts</p>
  </blockquote>
